            <h2>Key Achievements</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Policy advocacy, including contributions to disaster management policies in Himachal Pradesh and Uttarakhand.</li>
                <li>Establishing Disaster Management Resource Centers to enhance preparedness and response.</li>
                <li>Promoting sustainable livelihoods and conservation practices with a focus on climate-resilient approaches.</li>
                <li>Strengthening over 500 Panchayats across Himachal Pradesh and Uttarakhand to ensure inclusive growth.</li>
            </ul>
